仔 除非餵得份量多左（要磅份量否則好易痾爛屎）或轉味道<br />\n小小個人經驗 你可以試下 ziwipeak <br />\n但乾糧黎講佢係好鬼貴<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QtZTZEb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQtZTZEb.png&h=5ebc6bfb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"adb518ec0e16ecf4af42d7be1a19844836ceb39a","tid":2435631,"uid":156652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T09:31:55.000Z","msg":"睇醫生"},{"pid":"4369f8d23925649a7a24d0604ad6c323926ac1d6","tid":2435631,"uid":366624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T09:49:44.000Z","msg":"我隻貓之前都係咁 試左好多隻牌子罐都係軟便同爛屎 <br />\n真係只可以不斷試唔同牌子試到夾到為止 <br />\n而家如果我餵罐就會揀Animonda Carny或者Tiki Cat <br />\n但我好少餵濕糧 轉咗餵小怪獸隻太空凍乾做主食 <br />\n首要係隻貓肯食同鐘意食 唔係隻隻貓都肯 <br />\n成本同餵罐差唔多又健康啲<br />\n如果係無辦法之下我覺得你可以一試<br />\n<a href=\"https://litomon.com/product/rawmix_catfood/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flitomon.com%2Fproduct%2Frawmix_catfood%2F&d=vOSJ0XARgdQWnSR9BVy1n%2BIs%2Fr43DZ9KHrtYDEqBsnw%3D&h=cbc956d4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://litomon.com/product/rawmix_catfood/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cBuAtEi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcBuAtEi.png&h=0a62da25&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7bf6e969851c5fd2350aee5427bc8b7e870fc116","tid":2435631,"uid":50032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4369f8d23925649a7a24d0604ad6c323926ac1d6","tid":2435631,"uid":366624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T09:49:44.000Z","msg":"我隻貓之前都係咁 試左好多隻牌子罐都係軟便同爛屎 <br />\n真係只可以不斷試唔同牌子試到夾到為止 <br />\n而家如果我餵罐就會揀Animonda Carny或者Tiki Cat <br />\n但我好少餵濕糧 轉咗餵小怪獸隻太空凍乾做主食 <br />\n首要係隻貓肯食同鐘意食 唔係隻隻貓都肯 <br />\n成本同餵罐差唔多又健康啲<br />\n如果係無辦法之下我覺得你可以一試<br />\n<a href=\"https://litomon.com/product/rawmix_catfood/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flitomon.com%2Fproduct%2Frawmix_catfood%2F&d=vOSJ0XARgdQWnSR9BVy1n%2BIs%2Fr43DZ9KHrtYDEqBsnw%3D&h=cbc956d4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://litomon